short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Reads The Orders From Swiggy,Zomato to Honey bill.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This chrome extension is dedicated for the users of Honey Bill Software. This helps the users to capture orders from websites of Swiggy and Zomato and helps the user to save it to the Point Of Sale billing application. It minimizes the time to print the invoice.
